name: PrinceJ
description:
A city mayor who calls himself "Prince J" enforced some new rules that people are not rather happy with, creating chaos amongst them. Random fires start to appear, people violently going places, it's all looking helpless. Word gets spread there's a revolution coming, and Prince J's assistant comes up with the idea to discover the date of the event and go to it undercover to try to stop it. It all kinda goes according to plan until it doesn't. Try to put an end to this situation.

Extract the files and run "Brackeys.exe" to Play! Enjoy!
